---
import Me from "./Me.astro";
---

<section class="bg-primary">
  <div class="px-8 2xl:max-w-7xl mx-auto py-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 text-secondary gap-6 text-lg">
      <p
        class="text-3xl lg:col-span-3 lg:text-5xl indent-32 lg:indent-32 text-right"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="3000"
      >
        I’m an experienced software developer with a broad skill set and a
        proven track record in building robust applications. I work across
        technologies ranging from backend to frontend, databases and full-stack
        solutions. Over the years I have completed several successful projects,
        contributed to meaningful applications, and developed a deep
        understanding of software architecture, design and best practices.
      </p>
      <div
        class="text-1xl lg:col-span-1 lg:text-5xl indent-32 lg:indent-32"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="150"
        data-aos-duration="3000"
      >
        <Me />
      </div>
      <p
        class="text-lg lg:col-start-2 leading-relaxed"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="2500"
      >
        I am currently available for new projects. If you need a mobile
        application, backend service or a full-stack solution adapted to your
        needs, feel free to reach out: <a class="underline underline-offset-4" href="mailto:isc.rarroyo@gmail.com"
          >isc.rarroyo@gmail.com</a
        >
      </p>
      <p
        class="lg:col-start-4 leading-relaxed"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="2500"
      >
        As a dedicated developer, I offer a personalized and professional
        approach to software development, shaping solutions that meet both
        technical and business requirements. I deliver maintainable, efficient
        and scalable code with clear attention to detail and quality.
      </p>
      <p
        class="lg:col-start-4 leading-relaxed"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="3000"
      >
        My commitment to best practices, solid architecture and clean code
        ensures that each project not only works but also evolves sustainably. I
        strive to build software that grows with your needs, keeps performance
        stable and allows future expansion when required.
        <br /><br />
        With a broad understanding of full-stack development, database design, and
        modern tooling, I aim to deliver solutions that align with your business
        goals while offering a high level of reliability and maintainability.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-3xl lg:col-span-3 lg:text-7xl lg:col-start-2 lg:mt-48 indent-32 lg:indent-32"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="3000"
      >
        Let’s build software that solves real problems, scales with your vision
        and delivers lasting value to your users.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
